The Galaxy S8 offers a multitude of features packaged within cutting edge design.

This phone will be part of the corporate mobile contract, and you will not be billed for its use. The phone has the following technical specifications:

  • Android OS
  • Face detection
  • 4GB RAM (LPDDR4)
  • 8MP AF Camera Resolution Front
  • Dual Pixel 12MP AF Camera Resolution Back
  • Continuous autofocus video
